+							*getpackages()*
+getpackages([{pacname}, [{pactype}, [{plugname}]]])
+		Return a List of packages or plugins in fullpath.
+
+		{pacname} specifies a package name.  If it is not given or an
+		empty string, "*" is used.
+		{pactype} specifies a package type.  It can be "opt", "start",
+		"*" or "NONE".  If it is not given or an empty string, "*" is
+		used.  If "NONE" is specified only package directories are
+		listed.  Otherwise all plugin directories under the specified
+		packages are listed.
+		{plugname} specifies a plugin name.  If it is not given or an
+		empty string, "*" is used.
+		See: |packages|
+
